(2, 1, 'Language fika', 'logo_1435307921423.jpg', 'cover_1434289493043.png', 'Do you like to meet new people? Would you like to practice your Swedish? Anybody is invited to the Språkfika to sit down, have a coffee and speak Swedish for an hour or two. <br><br>When? 17:00-19:00 every second week (see dates in calendar) <br>Where? IM-office, Västgötagränd 17. OBS! Entrance from Fatbursparken<br><br>Summer 2015<br><br>thursday 25 juni<br>JULI - closed<br>tuesday 4 augusti<br>thursday 20 augusti<br><br>tuesday 1 september<br>thursday 17 september<br>tuesday 29 september<br>thursday 15 oktober<br>tuesday 27 oktober<br>thursday 12 november<br>tuesday 24 november<br>thursday 10 december<br><br>Website:&nbsp; http://www.manniskohjalp.se/node/2017<br>Contact: jonathan.osterlund@manniskohjalp.se <br>', 'Have coffee and practice your Swedish<br>', '<br>', 'http://www.manniskohjalp.se/node/2017', '', 'en', 0, 1, '2015-06-26 11:38:41'),
(3, 0, 'Läkare i Världen', 'logo_1435318529735.png', 'https://www.facebook.com/lakareivarlden?fref=ts', '<div><br></div>Clinic for undocumented migrants – on Wednesdays<br>Läkare i Världen (Doctors of the World) offers free medical services to EU-citizens and other migrants. There are doctors and nurses who receive patients. It is not a requirement to make an appointment prior to the visit. This healthcare is free of charge.<br><br>Every Wednesday evening 18.30-21.00<br>Where? Artemisgatan 10, Hjorthagen, Stockholm (Metro: Ropsten).<br>When? Every Wednesday evening from 18.30-21.00<br>Drop-in, no appointment needed.<br><br><div>Contact them for more details:<div>Phone: 08-664 66 87<br>Website: <a href="http://lakareivarlden.org/">http://lakareivarlden.org/</a></div><div>Email: info@lakareivarlden.org<div><br></div><div>To read about the law that gives all undocumented migrants right to health care:&nbsp;<a href="http://sjukutanpapper.nu">http://sjukutanpapper.nu</a></div><div><br><span style="font-weight: bold;">Counselling</span><br>For a good life situation and long term good health it is necessary to have basic security which includes the right of residence, housing and income.  Doctors of the World offers counselling with a focus on migration and asylum law. Human rights and especially the right to health are the basic guiding principles of this work.<br></div></div></div>', '<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana; font-size: 12px; text-align: start;">Free medical services for EU-citizens and migrants.</span></div>', 'Läkare i Världen (Doctors of the World) offers free medical services to EU-citizens and other migrants.<div><br></div>', 'http://lakareivarlden.org/', 'info@lakareivarlden.org', 'en', 40, 1, '2015-09-29 18:22:28'),
(4, 0, 'Newspaper 8 Sidor', 'logo_1435257228817.png', 'https://www.facebook.com/8sidor?fref=ts', '8 Sidor is a newspaper in easy-to-read and simple Swedish. <br><br>The letters are bigger than in a regular newspaper.<br>The sentences are shorter. <br>8 Sidor does not use advanced words.<br>8 Sidor explains what has happened, <br>where it happened and why it happened. <br><br>The newspaper is not dependent on a political party,<br>or an organisation.<br>The reporters are free to choose&nbsp;<div style="font-style: normal;">what news they believe are the most important to be told. <br></div><div style="font-style: normal;"><br></div><div style="font-style: normal;">Visit their website:&nbsp;<a href="http://8sidor.se">http://8sidor.se</a></div><div style="font-style: normal;"><br></div><div><span style="font-style: italic;">Text written by Stan för nyanlända.</span></div>', '8 Sidor is a newspaper in easy-to-read Swedish. <div><br></div>', 'News in easy-to-read Swedish.<div><br></div>', 'http://8sidor.se', '', 'en', 39, 1, '2015-09-29 18:20:27'),
