(83, 0, '400contacts', 'logo_1447667768650.png', 'www.facebook.com/400contacts', '<div style="font-style: normal;"><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br></span></div><span style="font-style: normal; font-weight: bold;">400contacts<br></span><br>400contacts is a mentoring program for professionals. We match refugees and local professionals based on geographic location, professional interests and career plans.<br><br>When there is a mentor and refugee match. We will send the refugee''s profile to the mentor''s email. The mentor can decide if they want to connect or not. The ultimate goal is to find a skilled job for the refugee in their new home country.<br><br><br><span style="font-style: italic;">Text written by 400contacts.</span>', 'We connect refugees with local professionals.', 'Connecting refugees with local professionals.<div><br></div>', 'http://www.400contacts.com', '400contacts@gmail.com', 'en', 0, 1, '2015-11-21 15:54:42');
